org.transitime.gtfs.gtfsStructs

Class GtfsRoute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.gtfs.gtfsStructs.GtfsBase
      • org.transitime.gtfs.gtfsStructs.GtfsRoute

  • @Immutable
public class GtfsRoute
extends GtfsBase
    A GTFS routes object. Contains two extension columns beyond the GTFS spec. These are rout.order and hidden. They are useful for the user interface. They will usually be set using a supplemental routes file.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
